{"tid":1387151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議黎緊嘅連儂牆/文宣全部集中「陪審團否決權」","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:38:10.000Z","uid":35870,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f20567298b81e2f014440ff02db025005dd983d","tid":1387151,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"首先，真係唔係好多人有聽過「陪審團否決權」呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n反而過去一段日子已經大量咁宣傳黑警政府惡行，相信要知嘅大眾都已經知道晒，而家要做嘅野，我覺得係諗方法全力拯救義士<br />\n<br />\n我希望，所有街道，所有連儂牆，所有可以貼野嘅地方都貼滿晒「陪審團否決權」呢樣野，要全香港所有有陪審團資格嘅人都知道係咩黎！！"},{"pid":"a8b82a20bb08d8479c83fb182d322361fabe127c","tid":1387151,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"【我係分化撚】 陪 審 團 否 決 權 係 笑 話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1387019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1387019</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1523aa2ba007d25826c73c66e73feb98f5af8746","tid":1387151,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"利伸：不鼓勵犯法行為，貼還貼唔好犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcf3f858c31c3fd2089e4aa2a6e4c66bbc61f2d","tid":1387151,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97b0f267bdbcd1c8f47473249d392cc7d9acaa5","tid":1387151,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:18:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862a1eaf662ca8a16e50a8104200147e725d05d4","tid":1387151,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73101fd9606eee485f17a8897efef913f9ad9584","tid":1387151,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/